<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff; /* Light theme background color */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333333; /* Light theme text color */
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff; /* Light theme container background */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; /* Light theme border color */
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; /* Light theme border color */
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 250px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #573298; /* Light theme primary color */
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #573298;
            color: #ffffff!important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #472280;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://common-assets.xkartindia.com/web-logo.png" alt="App Logo"> <!-- App logo -->
        <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi there,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password. If this was you, please click the button below to reset your password. If you didn’t make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <a href="<%= frontendBaseUrl %>/reset-password?token=<%= resetToken %>" class="button">Reset Your Password</a>
        <p>If you’re having trouble with the button above, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p><a href="<%= frontendBaseUrl %>/reset-password?token=<%= resetToken %>"><%= frontendBaseUrl %>/reset-password?token=<%= resetToken %></a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> VKRR Pvt Ltd. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
